{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"289bf0ca-d127-4ecc-8df4-8301ce18c5f8","content":"**You will need to change your target framework.** MSTest v4 dropped support for .NET 6.0 — it requires **.NET 8.0** or later (along with .NET Framework 4.6.2+).\n\n.NET 6 reached end-of-life in November 2024, so MSTest v4 only targets currently-supported TFMs.\n\nTo migrate, update your `TargetFramework` to at least `net8.0` and bump the MSTest package version:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n```\n```xml\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"4.0.0\" />\n```\n\nWould you like me to apply these changes to your project?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ad7ae2c1-d64c-41ad-ac7b-688475eabf08","outputTokens":180,"requestId":"67C8:163FFF:1C51693:1FF1F61:69FD5413"},"id":"6732b26c-8856-4976-9010-d11e01b42b38","timestamp":"2026-05-08T03:10:17.113Z","parentId":"04dc006a-b24d-40d0-92d4-d380b1bf5d81"}
